  line `14. Cl. (o) omitted by Act 37 of 1986, s. 11 (w.e.f. 10-2-1987).`
  line
  line `15. Subs. by Act 16 of 2021, s. 2, for "reconnaissance permit, prospecting license or mining lease" (w.e.f. 28-3-2021).`
