  line
  line `20. Subs. by Act 16 of 2023, s. 14, for the words, figures and letters "mining lease or composite licence under section 10B, 11,11A, 11B" (w.e.f. 17-8-2023).`
  line
  line `21. Cl. (qqh) omitted by Act 16 of 2021, s. 18 (w.e.f. 28-3-2021).`
  line
  line `22. Ins. by Act 25 of 2016, s. 4 (w.e.f. 6-5-2016).`
  line
  line `23. Cl. (qqk) omitted by Act 16 of 2021, s. 18 (w.e.f. 28-3-2021).`
